{
  "chapter": 1,
  "chapter_summary": "铁戟温侯吕南人近年声名赫赫，拥有寒铁双戟和火红宝马，娶武林第一美人薛若璧为妻。然而天争教主萧无以绝顶武功和智慧夺走其妻，并培植势力要铲除吕南人。吕南人在保定府外故意败给天争教金衣香主朱砂掌尤大君，以金丝背心硬接一掌后布置假死现场，跳入护城河逃脱，从此隐姓埋名化名江南秀才伊风。两年后他游历华山，在山阴处听到少女声音后与之发生误会交手，少女母亲孙敏赶到阻止。对话中少女提到天争教，伊风方知母女也是天争教仇敌——原来她们是三湘大侠凌北修的妻女凌琳和孙敏，凌北修被天争教金衣坛高手所伤不治。正当双方互疑之际，天争教金衣香主夺命双尸宫氏兄弟现身，要将孙敏带回天争教。伊风面临良心挣扎：出手相助恐暴露身份，不管又于心不安。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_nan_ren",
      "speaker_name": "吕南人",
      "listener": "char_you_da_jun",
      "text": "想不到吧？想不到我会从江南跑到此地来吧？",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 56,
      "line_end": 57
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_you_da_jun",
      "speaker_name": "尤大君",
      "listener": "char_lv_nan_ren",
      "text": "的确奇怪。",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 58,
      "line_end": 59
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_you_da_jun",
      "speaker_name": "尤大君",
      "listener": "char_lv_nan_ren",
      "text": "只是我奇怪的并不是你跑到这里来，而是你居然还敢在此露面。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 62,
      "line_end": 63
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_nan_ren",
      "speaker_name": "吕南人",
      "listener": "char_you_da_jun",
      "text": "我为什么不敢露面，难道我还怕你们？",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 66,
      "line_end": 66
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_nan_ren",
      "speaker_name": "吕南人",
      "listener": "char_you_da_jun",
      "text": "你们叫我吕南人无家可归，我也叫你们不得安宁，我在江南你们的老巢斗不不过你们，难道在这里我还怕了你们几个鼠辈！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 68,
      "line_end": 69
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_you_da_jun",
      "speaker_name": "尤大君",
      "listener": "char_lv_nan_ren",
      "text": "好！好！我姓尤的就叫你看看咱天争教在两河的力量！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 72,
      "line_end": 76
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_you_da_jun",
      "speaker_name": "尤大君",
      "listener": "char_lv_nan_ren",
      "text": "好朋友不去逃命，还想和天争教较较劲，那敢情是活得不耐烦了！姓吕的，你下来，让咱教训教训你！",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 78,
      "line_end": 80
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_nan_ren",
      "speaker_name": "吕南人",
      "listener": "char_you_da_jun",
      "text": "朋友，废话少说，亮'招子'，动手吧！",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 84,
      "line_end": 84
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_you_da_jun",
      "speaker_name": "尤大君",
      "listener": "char_lv_nan_ren",
      "text": "我姓尤的动手，还没有用过兵刃。",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 86,
      "line_end": 86
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_nan_ren",
      "speaker_name": "吕南人",
      "listener": "char_you_da_jun",
      "text": "跟你这种鼠辈动手，大爷也用不着动用兵刃。",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 94,
      "line_end": 94
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_you_da_jun",
      "speaker_name": "尤大君",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这小子中了我一掌，焉能还有命在？",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 140,
      "line_end": 140
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_you_da_jun",
      "speaker_name": "尤大君",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我们慢慢追去不迟，就等着去收他的尸好了。",
      "tone": "狂笑",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 142,
      "line_end": 142
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "女孩子",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "妈，他会掉下去吗？我看他也会武功呢！",
      "tone": "好奇",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 276,
      "line_end": 277
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yi_feng",
      "speaker_name": "伊风",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "在下伊风，偶游华山，是哪一位前辈高人出言，务请现身指教！",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 312,
      "line_end": 313
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yi_feng",
      "speaker_name": "伊风",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "朋友！你再也躲不了啦！是好汉，就出来！",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 386,
      "line_end": 386
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_er",
      "speaker_name": "少女",
      "listener": "char_yi_feng",
      "text": "出来就出来，有什么了不起！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 388,
      "line_end": 389
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_er",
      "speaker_name": "琳儿",
      "listener": "char_sun_min",
      "text": "妈！这人不是好东西，恐怕是来查探我们的，可绝不能放他走了！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 492,
      "line_end": 493
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_min",
      "speaker_name": "少妇",
      "listener": "char_lin_er",
      "text": "琳儿！先住手，让我问问他！",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 498,
      "line_end": 498
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_min",
      "speaker_name": "少妇",
      "listener": "char_yi_feng",
      "text": "朋友是哪里来的？到这里来是干什么？",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 502,
      "line_end": 503
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_min",
      "speaker_name": "少妇",
      "listener": "char_yi_feng",
      "text": "朋友到这华山来，若是想找我母女的晦气，那么，朋友！今天也别想再走出去了。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 510,
      "line_end": 512
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_er",
      "speaker_name": "少女",
      "listener": "char_sun_min",
      "text": "妈！这人鬼鬼祟祟地，在这里呆了三四个时辰还不走，又在我们这里东张西望的，一定是那家伙的狗腿子！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 518,
      "line_end": 519
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yi_feng",
      "speaker_name": "伊风",
      "listener": "char_sun_min",
      "text": "在下伊风，偶游华山，对两位绝无恶意。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 526,
      "line_end": 526
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_er",
      "speaker_name": "少女",
      "listener": "char_yi_feng",
      "text": "你偶游华山，可是你干什么要在这块地方一呆就是好几个时辰？难道这块地方有什么宝贝吗？",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 530,
      "line_end": 531
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_min",
      "speaker_name": "少妇",
      "listener": "char_yi_feng",
      "text": "以阁下的身手，该是江湖中成名立万的人物。可是'伊风'这名字，我却没有听人说过。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 534,
      "line_end": 535
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yi_feng",
      "speaker_name": "伊风",
      "listener": "char_sun_min",
      "text": "在下对两位确实没有恶意，也不知道两位是谁，两位如不相信，在下也无法解释。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 540,
      "line_end": 540
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yi_feng",
      "speaker_name": "伊风",
      "listener": "char_sun_min",
      "text": "老实说，在下也有难言之隐，两位如能体谅，在下也绝不会将有关今日之事说出去。",
      "tone": "恳求",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 544,
      "line_end": 545
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_min",
      "speaker_name": "少妇",
      "listener": "char_yi_feng",
      "text": "可是我们又怎能信得过你？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 552,
      "line_end": 553
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yi_feng",
      "speaker_name": "伊风",
      "listener": "char_sun_min",
      "text": "在下实是无意闯入华山，对两位更毫无企图，两位如不相信，在下也实在没有什么方法可以……",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 574,
      "line_end": 574
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_min",
      "speaker_name": "少妇",
      "listener": "char_yi_feng",
      "text": "只要你说出你实在的来历就行了。须知阁下虽有难言之隐，我母女也有不得已的苦衷。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 576,
      "line_end": 579
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yi_feng",
      "speaker_name": "伊风",
      "listener": "char_sun_min",
      "text": "我想两位必是避仇，只是在下的仇家，恐怕比两位的仇家还要厉害，在下实在……",
      "tone": "犹豫",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 582,
      "line_end": 582
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_er",
      "speaker_name": "少女",
      "listener": "char_yi_feng",
      "text": "你不愿意说是不是？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 584,
      "line_end": 584
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_er",
      "speaker_name": "少女",
      "listener": "char_sun_min",
      "text": "妈！您跟他罗嗦干什么？我看他说话吞吞吐吐，一定心怀鬼胎，说不定就是'天争教'下的狗腿子。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 586,
      "line_end": 587
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_shen",
      "speaker_name": "夺命双尸",
      "listener": "char_sun_min",
      "text": "凌夫人！我们教主想念你得很！久闻你是武林中的美人，怎么忍心让我们教主想得这么惨？",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 642,
      "line_end": 645
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_shen",
      "speaker_name": "夺命双尸",
      "listener": "char_sun_min",
      "text": "夫人！还是跟着我们一齐回去吧！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 650,
      "line_end": 651
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_er",
      "speaker_name": "凌琳",
      "listener": "char_gong_shen",
      "text": "你们两个怪物少废话，要找死，姑娘就送你们回老家去！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 654,
      "line_end": 655
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_shen",
      "speaker_name": "宫氏兄弟",
      "listener": "char_lin_er",
      "text": "怪物？这小姑娘说话真有意思，嗯！长大了和你妈妈一样，也是个美人。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 658,
      "line_end": 660
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_shen",
      "speaker_name": "宫申",
      "listener": "char_yi_feng",
      "text": "这位朋友像是和凌夫人也有些未了之事，不过那些事却冲着我兄弟的面上揭过了。朋友，你闪开！",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 668,
      "line_end": 671
    }
  ],
